                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890708-59-off287 t17890708-59-cd288"></join> last, four pewter pepper castors, value 2 s. eleven Queens metal tea spoons, value 11 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17890708-59-victim542" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Alderson
                  <interp inst="t17890708-59-victim542" type="surname" value="Alderson"></interp>
