                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890708-59-defend540 t17890708-59-punish292"></join>
               Privately whipped
            </rs>, and discharged.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
